channel.title: [Delta] My server doesn't have '::add model'?
channel.description:
Well i was trying to add a chaotic maul, And i go to do the command 'Add model' it didn't work so i did 'addmodel' 'model' it wasn't there.
How do i add 'Addmodel' to my game ?
I assumed it was in Client.java .
Thanks in advanced

item.title: [Delta] My server doesn't have '::add model'?
item.dc:creator: @DefinateX DefinateX
item.description:
@DefinateX wrote:

[quote=“The Wanderer, post:4, topic:407444”]Make sure you are typing the right number for the models you want to add? Say your gzip archive is named as 12563 you would type:
addmodel 12563
Then it would add it. I can’t remember if there is a space or not between add and model, since it has been ages since I’ve added models to a client. :P[/quote]

Yeah im typing the right model. (:… I searched for it in Client.java and couldn’t find it ? :S
